lead_paragraph: Sunderland manager David Moyes is targeting a quick second Premier League win after finally registering a belated first with the Black Cats at the 11th time of asking when his side beat Bournemouth last weekend.

headline.print_headline: Moyes Wants Quick Second Win After Belated First
